    <div class="overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 35vh">
      <div class="container px-5">
        <img src="/public/images/home_dashboard_preview.webp" class="img-fluid border border-dark rounded-3 shadow-lg mb-4" alt="Example image" width="700" height="600" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="b-divider"></div>
  <div class="px-4 border-bottom border-top bg-glass bg-glass-blue">
    <div class="container col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
      <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-5 py-5">
        <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-6">
          <img src="/public/images/home_responsive.webp" class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid" alt="Bootstrap Themes" width="600" height="400" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">
            Manage Satisfactory Servers On The Go!
          </h1>
          <p class="lead">
            SSM Cloud is a versatile platform that works
            seamlessly on multiple devices, including desktops,
            laptops, tablets, and smartphones. It automatically
            adapts to the device's screen, allowing you to
            manage servers and monitor performance on the go.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="b-divider"></div>
  <div class="px-4 border-bottom border-top bg-glass">
    <div class="container col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
      <div class="row flex-lg-row align-items-center g-5 py-5">
        <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-6">
          <img src="/public/images/home_notifications.webp" class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid" alt="Notifications" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">
            Get Notifications On Your Servers.
          </h1>
          <p class="lead">
            SSM Cloud offers a comprehensive notification system
            that enables users to stay informed about server
            updates, player activity, and other important
            events. It provides integration with external
            services like email, webhooks, and Discord which
            allows real-time notifications to be sent to you.
          </p>
          <p class="lead">
            This ensures that you are informed about server
            updates, player activity, or when the server has
            shut down or a new player joins the server. With
            these integrations, SSM Cloud can provide a
            convenient and efficient way for you to stay
            updated.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
